{"tid":1701110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(已FC) 全力支援屠龍小隊","createTime":"2019-11-09T00:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T05:53:18.000Z","uid":18245,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fbc10c93d7af9715f7302298d44e40336309a1f1","tid":1701110,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:38:13.000Z","msg":"TG:育龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Dragonteam2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDragonteam2019&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=08f120c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Dragonteam2019</a><br />\n<br />\n屠龍隊George:<br />\n黎緊2-3日<br />\n立場同蘋果會有澄清FC<br />\n<br />\n希望大家想捐就捐<br />\n唔捐都唔緊要<br />\n請不要再罵戰及捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n大家都係手足同陣營<br />\n勿傷和氣<br />\n我代我各隊員過往一日既粗劣態度表示抱歉<br />\n<br />\n好明大家係香港呢個氛圍下 難免會因無力感、壓力等而鬧情緒🙏🏻🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n正如大家所講 屠龍係一種精神<br />\n而我地都係貫徹呢個精神既小隊之一<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 #缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%AA-%E5%B1%A0%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A-%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E4%B9%9F%E5%88%B0%E7%93%B6%E9%A0%B8%E4%BA%86%E5%97%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A-%25E5%258B%2587%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E4%25B9%259F%25E5%2588%25B0%25E7%2593%25B6%25E9%25A0%25B8%25E4%25BA%2586%25E5%2597%258E%2F&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=baa4ef01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A-%25E5%258B%2587%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E4%25B9%259F%25E5%2588%25B0%25E7%2593%25B6%25E9%25A0%25B8%25E4%25BA%2586%25E5%2597%258E%2F&h=461f5f7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%AA-%E5%B1%A0%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A-%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E4%B9%9F%E5%88%B0%E7%93%B6%E9%A0%B8%E4%BA%86%E5%97%8E